課程概述 Course Description
       探討細胞生物之結構，功能及分化等知識 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
使學生具備細胞生物學專業知識建立學生溝通、討論的能力訓練學生邏輯思考的能力 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction of the course (II)2Cell junctions, Cell adhesion, ECM3Cell junctions, Cell adhesion, ECM4Discussion (Ch. 19)5Cancer6Discussion (Ch. 20)7Sexual reproduction8Development9Development10Discussion (Ch. 22)11Tissues, stem cells, tissue renewal12Tissues, stem cells, tissue renewal13Discussion (Ch. 23)14Pathogen/Infection/Immunity15Pathogen/Infection/Immunity16Pathogen/Infection/Immunity17Discussion (Ch. 24, 25)18Final Examination (30%) 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


